title: Bug 121682 - Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open the report
2. Navigate to the table containing highlight/map
3. Attempt to export the data in the table
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table containing highlight/map.
EB: When exporting the data from the table, the expected result is that the data is successfully exported. However, the actual result is that an exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
SR:
1. Open the report.
2. Navigate to the table containing highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data in the table.
